Leave your comments below.

96
00:04:41,069 --> 00:04:43,270
Thanks for watching this episode of China
Uncensored.

97
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:44,629
Once again I’m Chris Chappell.

98
00:04:44,629 --> 00:04:45,700
See you next time.

